  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Estimate if the use of a portable cardiac echograph for intra-hospital Emergencie improves
      the performances diagnose in the bed of patient in department of conventional medicine.

      The concordance between the initial medical diagnosis (previous the utilsation of portable
      echograph) and the final diagnosis (after portable echograph utisation) will be evaluated.
      These evaluation will be performed after retrospective review of the medical files
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
